{"prompt": "Generate a website for a travel agency. The website should be elegant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elegance Travel</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #A00000;\n            --secondary-color: #D00000;\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --background-color: #1A1A1A;\n            --hover-color: #E00000;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(160, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(160, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/000000/FFFFFF?text=Beautiful+Destinations') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5); /* Slightly darker overlay */\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: #2A2A2A;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .section h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .destinations {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .destination-card {\n            background-color: #3A3A3A;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .destination-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(160, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .destination-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .destination-card h4 {\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n            margin: 15px 0 10px 0;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .destination-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            padding: 0 10px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .social-links a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin: 0 10px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .social-links a:hover {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Elegance Travel</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#destinations\">Destinations</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Discover Your Dream Escape</h2>\n            <p>Curated journeys for the discerning traveler.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Plan Your Trip</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"destinations\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Our Signature Destinations</h3>\n            <div class=\"destinations\">\n                <div class=\"destination-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4A4A4A/FFFFFF?text=Paris\" alt=\"Paris\">\n                    <h4>Parisian Romance</h4>\n                    <p>Experience the city of lights with exclusive tours and charming accommodations.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"destination-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4A4A4A/FFFFFF?text=Kyoto\" alt=\"Kyoto\">\n                    <h4>Kyoto Serenity</h4>\n                    <p>Immerse yourself in the ancient traditions and breathtaking beauty of Japan.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"destination-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4A4A4A/FFFFFF?text=Santorini\" alt=\"Santorini\">\n                    <h4>Santorini Sunsets</h4>\n                    <p>Indulge in the iconic white-washed villages and stunning caldera views.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"destination-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4A4A4A/FFFFFF?text=Rome\" alt=\"Rome\">\n                    <h4>Roman Grandeur</h4>\n                    <p>Step back in time with a journey through history, art, and exquisite cuisine.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>About Elegance Travel</h3>\n            <p>At Elegance Travel, we believe that travel should be an experience of refined luxury and seamless comfort. Our passion lies in crafting bespoke itineraries that cater to your individual desires, transforming ordinary trips into extraordinary adventures. With meticulous attention to detail and a commitment to unparalleled service, we open the door to the world's most captivating destinations.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Contact Us</h3>\n            <p>Ready to embark on your next journey? Let us help you create memories that last a lifetime.</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@elegancetravel.com\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\">info@elegancetravel.com</a></p>\n            <p>Phone: <span style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\">+1 (800) 555-ELEG</span></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"social-links\">\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Facebook\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Instagram\"><i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Twitter\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a>\n        </div>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elegance Travel. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"https://kit.fontawesome.com/your-fontawesome-kit.js\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n    <script>\n        // Basic interactivity if needed in future, currently none required for static layout\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}